	a aprecia=E7=E3o dar-se-=E1 em fase =FAnica.</span></p>
	<p style=3D"text-align: justify; text-indent: 38px; margin: 15px 0cm">
	<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">
	<a name=3D"art165=A72"></a>=A7 2=BA=20
	O recurso de que trata o inciso I do <b>caput</b> deste artigo ser=E1 diri=
gido=20
