=20
	Administra=E7=E3o.</span></p>
	<p style=3D"text-align: justify; text-indent: 38px; margin: 15px 0cm">
	<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">
	<a name=3D"art174=A74"></a>=A7 4=BA=20
	O PNCP adotar=E1 o formato de dados abertos e observar=E1 as exig=EAncias=
=20
	previstas na <a href=3D"https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2011-201=
4/2011/Lei/L12527.htm">Lei n=BA 12.527, de 18 de novembro de 2011.</a></spa=
n></p>
	<p style=3D"text-align: justify; text-indent: 38px; margin: 15px 0cm">
	<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">
